133
00:06:53,700 --> 00:06:54,260
Hello.

134
00:06:54,280 --> 00:06:55,280
Hello, Mrs. Yang.

135
00:06:55,540 --> 00:06:56,360
My surname is Tian.

136
00:06:56,360 --> 00:06:57,690
You can call me Ms. Tian.

137
00:06:58,280 --> 00:06:59,210
Hello, Ms. Tian.

138
00:07:04,180 --> 00:07:06,240
Ms. Dong must have called you, right?

139
00:07:08,840 --> 00:07:10,200
Your lawyers

140
00:07:10,230 --> 00:07:11,610
are handling my divorce,

141
00:07:11,610 --> 00:07:13,170
which makes me your client.

142
00:07:13,470 --> 00:07:15,470
