145
00:07:23,150 --> 00:07:25,460
No matter how horrible Yang Weida is,

146
00:07:25,670 --> 00:07:28,330
we're husband and wife after all.

147
00:07:29,510 --> 00:07:32,110
Besides, we haven't officially divorced yet.

148
00:07:32,390 --> 00:07:34,850
So what happened later is very important to me.

149
00:07:34,850 --> 00:07:36,250
It's directly related to

150
00:07:36,340 --> 00:07:38,340
whether I can smoothly divorce him.

151
00:07:39,050 --> 00:07:40,110
More importantly,

152
00:07:40,790 --> 00:07:42,390
it will affect my interests.

153
00:07:44,670 --> 00:07:46,159
I know you have evidence.

154
00:07:46,620 --> 00:07:47,940
As your client,

155
00:07:48,270 --> 00:07:50,470
I want you to not disclose this evidence

156
00:07:50,640 --> 00:07:52,100
under any circumstances,

157
00:07:53,470 --> 00:07:54,730
or use it.

158
00:07:56,100 --> 00:07:58,980
As long as I can divorce him

159
00:07:59,000 --> 00:08:00,490
and take over our group,

160
00:08:01,320 --> 00:08:03,380
I'll offer you a significant reward.

161
00:08:04,540 --> 00:08:05,990
I'll entrust our group's legal affairs

162
00:08:05,990 --> 00:08:07,300
to your firm.

163
00:08:08,070 --> 00:08:08,950
As for the fees,

164
00:08:09,480 --> 00:08:10,720
you can name your price.

165
00:08:10,720 --> 00:08:11,980
We can talk about this.

166
00:08:14,470 --> 00:08:16,720
Thank you for your trust in our firm.

167
00:08:18,680 --> 00:08:22,930
But if Yang Weida is involved in the crime,

168
00:08:23,830 --> 00:08:26,750
we can't hide his evidence.

169
00:08:27,760 --> 00:08:29,730
