185
00:09:05,230 --> 00:09:06,690
I hope you can consider it.

186
00:09:07,960 --> 00:09:09,290
I'll wait for your call.

187
00:09:10,680 --> 00:09:11,200
Okay.

188
00:09:12,660 --> 00:09:14,190
