189
00:09:14,600 --> 00:09:15,130
See you.

190
00:09:30,270 --> 00:09:32,550
The choices are in front of us.

191
00:09:32,740 --> 00:09:36,010
On the one hand, it's an annual consultant fee of 1 million yuan.

192
00:09:36,010 --> 00:09:36,710
On the other hand, it's a case

193
00:09:36,710 --> 00:09:39,150
once it's revealed, it'll become a public prosecution.

194
00:09:39,150 --> 00:09:40,880
