00:37:15,140 --> 00:37:16,100
You're old.

858
00:37:17,220 --> 00:37:18,880
Your son is in college, right?

859
00:37:20,870 --> 00:37:22,200
Don't you feel ashamed?

860
00:37:23,430 --> 00:37:25,350
Didn't we warn you about that incident

861
00:37:25,350 --> 00:37:26,640
when Ms. Mei was here?

862
00:37:27,080 --> 00:37:28,110
It's only been a few years,

863
00:37:28,110 --> 00:37:29,240
and you did it again!

864
00:37:32,730 --> 00:37:34,500
I didn't do anything.

865
00:37:34,880 --> 00:37:36,160
What else do you want?

866
00:37:36,470 --> 00:37:38,470
Do you want to be the next Yang Weida?

867
00:37:38,890 --> 00:37:39,930
Don't say that.

868
00:37:40,220 --> 00:37:42,060
How could I do that?

869
00:37:42,080 --> 00:37:43,960
How about I play more recordings for you?

870
00:37:43,960 --> 00:37:45,160
Do you want to hear it?

871
00:37:52,310 --> 00:37:53,930
