872
00:37:53,930 --> 00:37:56,660
is enough for you to receive serious punishment.

873
00:37:56,930 --> 00:37:58,330
Do you still want to be a lawyer or not?

874
00:37:58,330 --> 00:37:59,870
Do you want your good reputation or not?

875
00:37:59,870 --> 00:38:01,730
How can you face your wife and son?

876
00:38:04,310 --> 00:38:05,500
You're so old.

877
00:38:05,810 --> 00:38:07,340
Once a jerk, always a jerk.

878
00:38:10,090 --> 00:38:10,980
I'm sorry.

879
00:38:11,890 --> 00:38:12,550
I was wrong.

880
00:38:17,470 --> 00:38:18,310
Listen.

881
00:38:18,870 --> 00:38:19,490
From now on,

882
00:38:19,490 --> 00:38:20,750
no female assistants.

883
00:38:23,670 --> 00:38:24,200
Let's go.

884
00:38:24,310 --> 00:38:25,040
Come with me.

885
00:38:27,790 --> 00:38:28,480
Where?

886
00:38:29,330 --> 00:38:30,410
Qiu Hua and her lawyer

887
00:38:30,410 --> 00:38:31,810
are waiting for you in my office.

888
00:38:31,810 --> 00:38:32,560
Her lawyer?

889
00:38:33,120 --> 00:38:34,360
She hired a lawyer?

890
00:38:38,660 --> 00:38:39,940
She hired a lawyer?

891
00:38:40,070 --> 00:38:40,670
Who?

892
00:38:41,950 --> 00:38:42,950
Luo Yingzi.

893
00:38:43,060 --> 00:38:44,420
Your good student.

894
00:38:45,250 --> 00:38:46,780
She's so amazing right now.

895
00:38:50,790 --> 00:38:51,990
They threatened you?

896
00:38:53,150 --> 00:38:55,310
These two women are united

897
00:38:55,870 --> 00:38:58,400
and disregard the senior lawyers in the firm.

898
00:38:58,950 --> 00:39:00,690
They've only been here for a few days.

899
00:39:00,690 --> 00:39:01,700
Other first-year lawyers don't have a case yet

900
00:39:01,700 --> 00:39:04,050
and they're looking for a case desperately.

901
00:39:04,050 --> 00:39:05,800
They already have an office.

902
00:39:05,930 --> 00:39:07,790
Did you see how arrogant they are?

903
00:39:08,240 --> 00:39:09,860
They can disrespect me today,

904
00:39:09,860 --> 00:39:12,260
and so can they disrespect you tomorrow.

905
00:39:12,360 --> 00:39:14,490
Is our firm still good enough for them?

906
00:39:15,870 --> 00:39:17,730
What's the point of saying those?

907
00:39:17,980 --> 00:39:19,350
It's your fault.

908
00:39:19,990 --> 00:39:21,580
Now, apologize

909
00:39:21,820 --> 00:39:23,320
to Qiu Hua.

910
00:39:23,800 --> 00:39:25,320
Apologize to them?

911
00:39:25,960 --> 00:39:27,160
What else do you want?

912
00:39:28,500 --> 00:39:30,980
Are you just going to watch them push their luck?

913
00:39:30,980 --> 00:39:31,900
I have to.

914
00:39:32,060 --> 00:39:33,310
You did it yourself.

915
00:39:37,600 --> 00:39:38,230
They said

916
00:39:38,370 --> 00:39:40,550
that they would go to the police if you didn't apologize.

917
00:39:40,550 --> 00:39:42,350
You'll be ruined then.

918
00:39:44,630 --> 00:39:46,460
Let them call the police if they have the guts.

919
00:39:46,460 --> 00:39:47,260
Let them go.

920
00:39:48,470 --> 00:39:49,730
You're so awesome now.

921
00:39:51,490 --> 00:39:53,050
I’m going to tell them that.

922
00:39:59,090 --> 00:39:59,930
Mrs. Fang.

923
00:40:00,550 --> 00:40:01,590
Mrs. Fang!

924
00:40:02,160 --> 00:40:03,020
Mrs... Fang...

925
00:40:07,270 --> 00:40:08,390
Sorry, Qiu Hua.

926
00:40:10,740 --> 00:40:12,790
I was careless

927
00:40:13,200 --> 00:40:14,770
and behaved inappropriately.

928
00:40:14,770 --> 00:40:16,360
which caused you pain.

929
00:40:17,010 --> 00:40:18,020
I apologize.

930
00:40:18,500 --> 00:40:19,900
You didn't make it clear.

931
00:40:22,200 --> 00:40:24,040
Tell us what you did to Qiu Hua.

932
00:40:33,860 --> 00:40:35,820
S-S-Sorry, Qiu Hua.

933
00:40:38,530 --> 00:40:40,750
M-M-My behavior...

934
00:40:43,270 --> 00:40:43,890
may have

935
00:40:44,310 --> 00:40:46,110
caused you a misunderstanding.

936
00:40:47,740 --> 00:40:48,850
