937
00:40:48,850 --> 00:40:49,330
Well.

938
00:40:50,600 --> 00:40:52,090
It was sexual harassment.

939
00:40:52,370 --> 00:40:54,410
Is it sexual harassment or not?

940
00:41:07,110 --> 00:41:08,180
Sorry, Qiu Hua.

941
00:41:10,280 --> 00:41:10,830
I...

942
00:41:11,720 --> 00:41:12,910
I have

943
00:41:13,360 --> 00:41:15,170
sexually harassed you.

944
00:41:17,350 --> 00:41:18,620
I apologize.

945
00:41:31,160 --> 00:41:31,870
Qiu Hua.

946
00:41:32,780 --> 00:41:35,740
Mr. Han, as a senior lawyer,

947
00:41:35,930 --> 00:41:37,750
has formally apologized to you.

948
00:41:38,310 --> 00:41:38,990
Accept it.

949
00:41:41,210 --> 00:41:42,240
Besides, Han,

950
00:41:42,290 --> 00:41:43,760
give the cases in your hands

951
00:41:43,760 --> 00:41:46,320
that were mainly handled by Qiu Hua back to her.

952
00:41:46,320 --> 00:41:47,160
Wh-Wh-What?

953
00:41:47,550 --> 00:41:49,700
This is one of the conditions.

954
00:41:56,560 --> 00:41:57,890
And a letter of apology.

955
00:41:58,910 --> 00:41:59,640
What?

956
00:42:00,390 --> 00:42:02,370
They asked you to write a letter of apology

957
00:42:02,370 --> 00:42:03,830
so that Qiu Hua can keep it.

958
00:42:04,010 --> 00:42:05,560
No, I can't write this.

959
00:42:08,740 --> 00:42:09,780
Qiu Hua.

960
00:42:10,860 --> 00:42:12,950
I kept you in the firm.

961
00:42:13,010 --> 00:42:15,340
Without me, you wouldn't have found a job.

962
00:42:16,230 --> 00:42:18,150
Although I made some mistakes,

963
00:42:18,840 --> 00:42:21,030
you can't chase me into a dead corner.

964
00:42:22,510 --> 00:42:24,180
I'm an old man.

965
00:42:24,480 --> 00:42:28,010
I won't be able to live with myself if I leave you something on me.

966
00:42:33,830 --> 00:42:34,460
Qiu Hua.

967
00:42:35,750 --> 00:42:37,760
I believe he won't do it again.

968
00:42:39,150 --> 00:42:40,250
I'm here

969
00:42:40,620 --> 00:42:42,350
witnessing everything today.

970
00:42:42,690 --> 00:42:43,890
I can testify for you.

971
00:42:44,930 --> 00:42:46,460
Please let him off the hook.

972
00:42:53,880 --> 00:42:54,530
Qiu Hua.

973
00:42:55,620 --> 00:42:56,350
Don't worry.

974
00:42:57,100 --> 00:42:58,380
I recorded everything he said.
